PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780138973
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'proud' D-Day veteran
OL,4,CAlec Penstone following death aged 101
OL,6,FThe Isle of Wight branch of the
OL,7,FParachute Regimental Association
OL,8,Fposted on Facebook: "Alec was one of
OL,9,Fthe last remaining members of the
OL,10,Fgeneration who answered their
OL,11,Fcountry's call during the Second World
OL,12,FWar.
OL,14,F"Beginning his service in the Royal
OL,15,FNavy in 1943, he served through some
OL,16,Fof the war's most significant moments,
OL,17,Fincluding the preparations for D-Day
OL,18,Faboard HMS Campania, before continuing
OL,19,Fhis service in the Far East until his
OL,20,Fdemobilisation in 1946."
OL,26,@pD@UOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780138973
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'proud' D-Day veteran
OL,4,CAlec Penstone following death aged 101
OL,6,FThe branch continued: "Throughout his
OL,7,Flife, Alec remained dedicated to
OL,8,Fremembering those who never returned.
OL,10,F"As recently as the 80th anniversary
OL,11,Fof D-Day, he travelled to Normandy to
OL,12,Fhonour his fallen comrades, reminding
OL,13,Fus all that their sacrifice must never
OL,14,Fever be forgotten.
OL,16,F"Alec was a proud member of the Isle
OL,17,Fof Wight's veteran community and
OL,18,Fremained closely connected to his
OL,19,Ffellow servicemen and women throughout
OL,20,Fhis remarkable life.
OL,26,@nD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780138973
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'proud' D-Day veteran
OL,4,CAlec Penstone following death aged 101
OL,6,F"His courage, honesty, and commitment
OL,7,Fto the values for which his generation
OL,8,Ffought earned him the respect of all
OL,9,Fwho knew him.
OL,11,F"The members of the Parachute
OL,12,FRegimental Association Isle of Wight
OL,13,Fbranch extend our sincere condolences
OL,14,Fto Alec's family, friends, and
OL,15,Fcomrades in the Royal Naval
OL,16,FAssociation and wider armed forces
OL,17,Ffamily."
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
