PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780138973
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'proud' D-Day veteran
OL,4,CAlec Penstone following death aged 101
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Press Association in
OL,7,F2024, Mr Penstone said: "When I
OL,8,Frealised how many wonderful shipmates
OL,9,Fof mine died, and I just wonder why
OL,10,FI'm still spared.
OL,12,F"But nevertheless it was something
OL,13,Fthat's got to be down in history and
OL,14,Fmust never ever be forgotten."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
